{"tid":95435,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"備五百元果籃探林敏驄 張如城拜年收章魚阿媽扯火","createTime":"2017-01-26T04:42:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T12:30:21.000Z","uid":37827,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b7352093a84c8df069ca98fb419d1c00f7cbad1f","tid":95435,"uid":37827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T04:42:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/entertainment/art/20020214/2434023\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fentertainment%2Fart%2F20020214%2F2434023&d=SgZWlur5bQtibB4g4sFBT38C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=2ee7c278\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fentertainment%2Fart%2F20020214%2F2434023&h=fa662529\" target=\"_blank\">hk.apple.nextmedia.com/entertainment/art/20020214/2434023</a><br />\n張如城日前到林敏驄的家拜年，林敏驄為了搞氣氛，特別準備了一隻章魚作回禮，但此舉卻激怒了張如城的母親，她即時將章魚丟進垃圾桶，更表示家族所改的名字不應拿來開玩笑。<br />\n<br />\n[img]<a href=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/250pix/20020214/Article_ent/14ec2p2.jpg[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2F250pix%2F20020214%2FArticle_ent%2F14ec2p2.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=SgZWlur5bQtibB4g4sFBT38C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=01725e50\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2F250pix%2F20020214%2FArticle_ent%2F14ec2p2.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D&h=507a98b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/250pix/20020214/Article_ent/14ec2p2.jpg[/img]</a><br />\n林敏聰送章魚及玩具利是給張如城做回禮。<br />\n <br />\n[img]<a href=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/250pix/20020214/Article_ent/14ec2p3.jpg[/img]張如城送果籃給林敏聰拜年。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2F250pix%2F20020214%2FArticle_ent%2F14ec2p3.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D%E5%BC%B5%E5%A6%82%E5%9F%8E%E9%80%81%E6%9E%9C%E7%B1%83%E7%B5%A6%E6%9E%97%E6%95%8F%E8%81%B0%E6%8B%9C%E5%B9%B4%E3%80%82&d=SgZWlur5bQtibB4g4sFBT38C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=ce8281b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2F250pix%2F20020214%2FArticle_ent%2F14ec2p3.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D%E5%BC%B5%E5%A6%82%E5%9F%8E%E9%80%81%E6%9E%9C%E7%B1%83%E7%B5%A6%E6%9E%97%E6%95%8F%E8%81%B0%E6%8B%9C%E5%B9%B4%E3%80%82&h=52811837\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/250pix/20020214/Article_ent/14ec2p3.jpg[/img]張如城送果籃給林敏聰拜年。</a><br />\n <br />\n張如城的母親（左二）一向不愛面對鏡頭。　資料圖片<br />\n自封「亞洲神童」的十四歲歌手張如城，因無搞笑節目《香港鬆一鬆》而與林敏驄（阿驄）相識，今個農曆新年，張如城到林敏驄的家拜年，而阿驄更一早度定了一些搞笑位，買了一隻章魚作為給張如城的回禮。 <br />\n當日張如城在母親的陪同下，專程了一件賀年衫，並花了五百多元買了一個果籃，張如城的母親沿途亦不停教兒子講一些吉利的賀年說話。<br />\n<br />\n收玩具利是錢<br />\n兩人抵達林敏驄的住所，張如城送上果籃，阿驄於是給了張如城一封利是，但利是封內的卻不是真錢，而是其子林肯的玩具利是錢。阿驄其後說：「等我送番回禮畀你啦！」然後他拿出一早準備好、綁了大蝴蝶結的章魚出來。 <br />\n張如城一見到章魚，即時笑得合不攏嘴，但此舉動卻激怒了張如城的母親，她一手搶過章魚，並不停說：「唔好睇、唔好睇，丟佢、丟佢！」然後她走入阿驄的廚房，將章魚丟進垃圾桶，令到現場氣氛十分尷尬。<br />\n<br />\n家族名不能玩<br />\n阿驄見狀，立即在旁解釋說：「我送章魚畀佢做回禮，只係張如城個名諧音，而且想佢好似章魚咁，八足咁多爪，都係好意頭！」不過張如城的母親說：「唔可以，如城個名係家族改，係唔可以玩！」 <br />\n林敏驄與張如城原本打算一同拍新年照，結果弄得不歡而散，張如城的母親亦打算離開，但張如城仍一臉天真地對母親說：「我未食年糕喎，我想食埋年糕先至走！」 <br />\n張如城和母親離開後，林敏驄向記者說：「我本來諗住拜年開開心心，不過算啦，好少事，我心目中，佢（指張如城）永遠都係亞洲神童。」 <br />\n採訪、攝影：盧雪琪"},{"pid":"e7237b729c6427a2f9ded7f51da4795297d4b9e0","tid":95435,"uid":37827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T04:42:58.000Z","msg":"屌 貼圖貼唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a4854f49ffc35a64c214848d3414c771c2a1d86","tid":95435,"uid":66566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T04:44:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" clas